briefdescription.para: This function configures the TIM4 as a time base source. The time source is configured to have 1ms time base with a dedicated Tick interrupt priority.

simplesect.para: This function is called automatically at the beginning of program after reset by HAL_Init() or at any time when clock is configured, by HAL_RCC_ClockConfig().
Disable the tick increment by disabling TIM4 update interrupt.
Enable the tick increment by Enabling TIM4 update interrupt.
